      "raw_text": "by Mr.. Farrell is the most responsible\nono on the coast, as he will prac-\nticaNy control the oriental trade of\nthe Northern Securities system.\n\n\nJohn ID. Farrell was born In 1856\nand has worked his way from the\nranks. beginning as track laborer. He\nwas stationed in Spokane as superin-\ntendent of the Cascade division OF the\nGreat Northern in 1898. resigning\nto look after mining interests. Three\nyears ago he accepted the presidency\nof the Pacific Coast company and\nsince then has resided in Seattle.\n\n\nMIR. Farrell is most popular In Spo-\nkane and his many friends congratu-\nlate him upon his promotion."
